column1:
Well, we've confirmed the presence of
the Jail. Next, we look into Alice and any
potential victims.
And how do we do that? Look into what?

The usual rumor mills, lookin' for anything
about Alice. Gossip about her being abusive,
or other messed up stuff.

Good idea. Let's gather any intel that we can,
both online and on the streets.

But if we're ever to gain conclusive proof of
any rumors, I believe we'll need direct access
to her at some point...

Direct access to a pop star sounds awfully
tough...

Uh, about that... I may get to meet Alice
tomorrow?

Well, I had asked the modeling agency's
president if I could meet her sometime.

I heard she'd be on a TV show filming nearby,
so I asked if I could visit the set. I was hoping
to learn from her by watching her in action...

I gave up on it after making plans with you
guys, but I might be able to get the ball
rolling again in time...
The timing's nothing short of kismet...
Yeah! Way to go, Lady Ann!

But I'm not making any promises about it.
And there's no way we'd get to approach
her, either.

Plus, our full group's just too big. The most
I could even ask to bring is just one more
person...
I think I was just volunteered...

Welp! That settles that. We're counting on ya,
[1B]S1!

Give Alice shit when you meet her so you
can get some evidence out of her.
Ooh, you really are ready for this!
I dunno... Try hitting on her?

Idiot, her manager'll be right there too! She's
not gonna pay us any attention anyway.

Hey you'd better not be thinking of trying
anything funny! I'm the one who'll suffer
for it.

I think I'll tag along with you. We'll be fine
so long as no one sees me.
For today, let's focus on her potential victims.
